text: Wuyi New Area was established on June 26, 2012 in Nanping, Fujian. == Administration == * Wuyishan * part of Jianyang: Tancheng Subdistrict, Tongyou Subdistrict, Jiangkou Town, Jukou Town, Huangkeng Town and Chongluo Township. == See also == * Tianfu New Area * Fuzhou New Area Category:Populated places in Fujian
title: Wuyi New Area
